00:00:42,304 --> 00:00:45,690
Specifically, specifically, people as meat in video games.

8
00:00:47,174 --> 00:00:50,878
I should probably back up. Hi, I'm Tyreek. Nice to meet you.

9
00:00:51,719 --> 00:00:55,463
I'm a pixel artist, animator, coder, I guess, currently

