question, which is, when was the last time you played a game

14
00:01:06,415 --> 00:01:09,018
where you felt like you were inhabiting a human body?

15
00:01:09,913 --> 00:01:11,734
Not just controlling a collection of numbers.

16
00:01:12,155 --> 00:01:13,936
And I also don't mean like,

17
00:01:14,276 --> 00:01:16,178
oh yeah, this is a really well-written character,

