00:11:32,531 --> 00:11:35,194
and blast off their arms and legs and heads, but there are very few

231
00:11:35,895 --> 00:11:39,858
where I, as a human character, could undergo those same traumas.

232
00:11:41,079 --> 00:11:45,724
The meat feel wasn't relegated only to enemies, but was applied to myself as well in Ivan.

233
00:11:46,527 --> 00:11:48,828
And it was important for me to see that the player isn't

234
00:11:48,908 --> 00:11:52,611
represented as a robot or a mech or anything else where it

235
00:11:52,631 --> 00:11:53,412
would make sense.

236
00:11:53,552 --> 00:11:55,073
Oh, yeah, you get your arm blown off.

237
00:11:55,133 --> 00:11:57,575
You can just get a new one attached.

238
00:11:57,995 --> 00:12:05,261
Like, they're represented as a human character, a person that

239
00:12:05,281 --> 00:12:07,182
can be destroyed bit by bit or all at once.

240
00:12:08,130 --> 00:12:10,211
But like I said, the game's got a comedic vibe to it.

